  <source>Novartis</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The primary purpose of this trial is to evaluate whether the investigational medication is
      safe, effective and has the ability to increase spine bone density in osteogenesis imperfecta
      (OI) patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
